fields.content: Just pushed a hotfix for the SPIRITS telemetry ingest; seeing much cleaner data now.
Anyone else experiencing intermittent SoC disconnects? Trying to isolate if it's network or a specific device firmware issue.
We're rolling out OIDC integration for partner access next week. Keep an eye on the documentation updates.
Just got confirmation, our NQR compliance for the Q3 audit is looking solid.
The ConnectOS update for the in-store displays is scheduled for Tuesday night. Expect minor downtime.
Need to schedule a sync on the Q4 roadmap for the Barrows Connected Stores initiative. Let me know your availability.
Received a report about a power fluctuation affecting the POS terminals in the downtown branch. Investigating.

Thinking about standardizing OIDC flows across all partner integrations to simplify onboarding.

Looking into optimizing the SPIRITS data pipeline for real-time inventory updates.
